OL,3,CBritish Museum calls for donations to
OL,4,Csave Tudor pendant linked to Henry VIII
OL,6,FThe British Museum is aiming to raise
OL,7,F#3.5 million to save a gold pendant
OL,8,Flinked to Henry VIII's marriage to
OL,9,FKatherine of Aragon.
OL,11,FThe London museum says there are very
OL,12,Ffew surviving artefacts relating to
OL,13,Fthe pair's marriage and it has now
OL,14,Fbeen given the chance to acquire the
OL,15,FTudor Heart, which was discovered by a
OL,16,Fmetal detectorist in 2019, before it
OL,17,Fenters a private collection.
