OL,3,CBritish Museum calls for donations to
OL,4,Csave Tudor pendant linked to Henry VIII
OL,6,FTo acquire the pendant, the British
OL,7,FMuseum aims to raise #3.5 million by
OL,8,FApril 2026, and has already received a
OL,9,F#500,000 donation from The Julia
OL,10,FRausing Trust, as it calls for help
OL,11,Ffrom the public.
OL,13,FNicholas Cullinan, director of the
OL,14,FBritish Museum, said: "The Tudor Heart
OL,15,Fis perhaps one of the most incredible
OL,16,Fpieces of English history to have ever
OL,17,Fbeen unearthed.
