OL,6,F"Support will ensure that this unique
OL,7,Fand beautiful treasure is secured for
OL,8,Fthe nation, so that it can be enjoyed
OL,9,Fby and inspire generations to come."
OL,11,FAccording to the research by the
OL,12,Fmuseum, the 24 carat gold artefact may
OL,13,Fhave been created for a tournament
OL,14,Fheld in October 1518 to mark the
OL,15,Fbetrothal of their daughter, Princess
OL,16,FMary, to the French heir apparent.
