OL,3,CBritish Museum calls for donations to
OL,4,Csave Tudor pendant linked to Henry VIII
OL,6,FAfter it was found in a Warwickshire
OL,7,Ffield, the pendant was reported under
OL,8,Fthe Treasure Act 1996, which gives
OL,9,Fmuseums and galleries in England a
OL,10,Fchance to acquire historical objects
OL,11,Fand put them on display.
OL,13,FSimon Fourmy, chief executive of The
OL,14,FJulia Rausing Trust, said: "We are
OL,15,Fdelighted to support the British
OL,16,FMuseum in acquiring the Tudor Heart
OL,17,Ffor the nation.
