OL,3,CBritish Museum calls for donations to
OL,4,Csave Tudor pendant linked to Henry VIII
OL,6,F"This remarkable pendant sheds light
OL,7,Fon a defining royal marriage and
OL,8,Fenriches our understanding of the
OL,9,FTudor world.
OL,11,F"We hope others will be as inspired by
OL,12,Fthis extraordinary object as we were,
OL,13,Fand will join us in giving generously
OL,14,Fto ensure this treasure remains on
OL,15,Fview for many years to come."
OL,17,FA public campaign is now open for
OL,18,Fdonations, while the object will go on
OL,19,Fdisplay in the museum's gallery two
OL,20,Funtil April 2026.
